		</div>
		
		<div class="twitter">
			<a href="http://twitter.com/share" class="twitter-share-button" data-count="horizontal" data-text="Bitcoin: An Innovative  Alternative Digital Currency" data-url="http://hstlj.org/articles/bitcoin-an-innovative-alternative-digital-currency/" data-via="hstlj">Tweet</a><script type="text/javascript" src="http://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js"></script>
