<div>
<p><em>      </em>[62]<em>.   See </em>Mike Stathis, <em>Fool’s Gold (Part 1)</em>, Seeking Alpha (July 10, 2009), http://seekingalpha.com/‌article/148106-fool-s-gold-part-1; <em>Perma-Bears and Gold Bugs</em>, Continental Capital Advisors, LLC (Aug. 14, 2009), http://www.continentalca.com/‌home/‌August-14-2009.</p>
